The paper describes a web-based groupware application that supports the review process for technical contributions to conferences. This involves storing author information, abstracts, papers, and reviews, generating overviews based on reviews, and facilitating communication between reviewers to resolve conflicts. These tasks are related to several sub-categories of computer science, including cybernetics (cs.CY), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE).
